query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS capabilityAssessments (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  projectId INT NOT NULL,
  capabilityId INT NOT NULL,
  catalogReferenceId VARCHAR(50),
  maturityModelId VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  maturityScore DECIMAL(3,2),
  maturityLevel ENUM('initial','developing','defined','managed','optimizing'),
  targetMaturityLevel ENUM('initial','developing','defined','managed','optimizing'),
  dimensionScores JSON,
  maturityNarrative TEXT,
  keyStrengths JSON,
  keyGaps JSON,
  recommendations JSON,
  assessmentCompletedAt TIMESTAMP,
  assessedBy INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX capability_assessments_project_idx (projectId),
  INDEX capability_assessments_capability_idx (capabilityId),
  UNIQUE KEY capability_assessments_unique (projectId, capabilityId),
  FOREIGN KEY (projectId) REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (capabilityId) REFERENCES businessCapabilities(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (assessedBy) REFERENCES users(id)
)
